author: Unity
description:
Unity's Joy Horvath provides an overview of how to use MagikaVoxel to model, animate and incorporate your voxel art into your Unity workflow.

Download MagikaVoxel here: https://ephtracy.github.io/
Learn how to import assets in Unity: https://learn.unity.com/tutorial/importing-assets-2019-3
Get started with Animation in Unity: https://learn.unity.com/pathway/creative-core/unit/animation/tutorial/66fc66f1edbc2a0094cf3a8c
title: Modeling, texturing, animating and importing to Unity with MagikaVoxel | The Joy of Video Game Art
